{"tid":13788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[上水之苦]每月總有數日的離奇大塞車","createTime":"2016-11-30T08:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T12:55:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"366eeefb58b9c2b2e0c6db3d72de59e1b5be7a88","tid":13788,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6n0ldh1c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6n0ldh1c&h=7ceeee56&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0bs8qd1w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0bs8qd1w&h=254bb5bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j10wdemh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj10wdemh&h=f1f8e718&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上水又出現每月總有數日的離奇大塞車！傍晚6時許，上水一帶多處出現交通擠塞，但原因不明。長長車龍佔據大小馬路，包括上水港鐵站附近的新運路、寶石湖路、彩園路，以及粉嶺公路近彩園邨、掃管埔路、馬會道及龍琛路等。在上水港鐵站，巴士、小巴均受阻未能埋站上客，大批市民在車巴站外排隊等候，人龍打蛇餅。塞車近4小時後，至約10時半，運輸署宣布交通已恢復正常。 <br />\n<br />\n讀者黎先生指，他傍晚6時乘巴士，由翠麗花園往上水港鐵站，通常車程只需15分鐘，但他至晚上7時30分仍未到抵目的地。他又指，上水一帶經常塞車，不過今日特別嚴重，「平時塞一個鐘，依家塞2,3個鐘」。 <br />\n<br />\n有居民指，該區每月總有數日會出現類似的離奇大塞車情況。一眾網民亦鬧爆塞車，指一直未見有相關部門處理，又勸喻他人改乘地鐵前往上水。更有網民指，塞車可列入上水奇景之一。"},{"pid":"d723807f484854ea989352276da78bb382c74432","tid":13788,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:33:12.000Z","msg":"呢一兩年真係成日見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76195161bdb38821ea3c8b35225e2050041529b6","tid":13788,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"我已經唔係成日返入去，都總會間唔中見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7d431d7e174ab31c24228c92544dab320d1abc","tid":13788,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c13ec349612d3b71aa28a83f222525cbaccaccc","tid":13788,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f47ef7528f0b5f6c0899f02c59c8e953d362325","tid":13788,"uid":7659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"慘不忍睹"},{"pid":"abcb1d86b3727ff1fe7d3f6be8d4c933890336de","tid":13788,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"依家仲住上水本身已經係自己攞黎衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早10年就話姐，依家根本唔撚係比香港人住<br />\n利申：住左上水20年，頂唔順搬左出荃灣"},{"pid":"49445bcfdabd008b46a36128978af617a6772686","tid":13788,"uid":12343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"真係唔明點解可以咁撚塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}